Name: Barro 2020
About the game: Barro 2020 is the sequel for Barro with 8 new challenging race tracks. Game modes: Arcade: You vs 3 opponents, do your best and finish the race as the winner. Time trial: You against yourself, finish the laps as fastest as you can. Multiplayer: Play the multiplayer (split screen) with a friend and have fun. Cars: 4 types of cars, choose the one that fits you better.
